      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a bowl and cover with<strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Set aside for 12-15 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, drain the<strong> softened</strong> <strong>noodles</strong> and set aside</p>",
