            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, carefully pour away the oil from the reserved pan</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat, then add the <strong>crispy tofu</strong>, <strong>spicy Korean-style sauce</strong> and your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce has thickened and the tofu is coated – this is your<strong> sesame Korean-style tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
