        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> spicy rice noodle soup</strong> in a bowl and top with the<strong> sesame Korean-style tofu</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
